{"data":[{"date":"07:40 26/06","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ch\u1eedi b\u1edbi VAR sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/huyen-thoai-nuoc-anh-chui-boi-var-sau-tran-hoa-cua-bo-dao-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u1ede tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Seleccao, \u0110T Iran \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n \u1edf ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, v\u00e0 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Alan Shearer ch\u1eedi b\u1edbi VAR v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.\r\n</h2><h2><br />\r\nShearer ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch VAR<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1eef b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eedi th\u1ec1, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ed1 b\u1ecbch&rdquo; &ndash; Alan Shearer b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd b\u1ecb g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Cedric Soares \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m tay trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, v\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i sau khi theo d\u00f5i b\u0103ng h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, Shearer cho r\u1eb1ng VAR \u0111ang b\u1ecb l\u1ea1m d\u1ee5ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e0. Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t anh ch\u00e0ng r\u1ea5t may m\u1eafn, b\u1edfi n\u1ebfu Iran ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t khung c\u1ea3nh v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n. Th\u00fa th\u1ef1c, t\u00f4i ch\u1eb3ng hi\u1ec3u v\u00ec sao anh ta quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n.&rdquo;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;N\u1ebfu anh ta nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh quay ch\u1eadm, v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u00edch, anh ta l\u00e0 th\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u00ean. Ch\u1eb3ng l\u1ebd b\u1ea1n th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n trong b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 l\u00fac n\u00e0o h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1m tay v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng? Cedric Soares kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3. Anh ta c\u00e1ch n\u1eeda met v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4i m\u1eaft \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm nghi\u1ec1n.&rdquo;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alan Shearer ch\u1eedi b\u1edbi VAR sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alan Shearer ch\u1eedi b\u1edbi VAR sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/huyen-thoai-nuoc-anh-chui-boi-var-sau-tran-hoa-cua-bo-dao-nha.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alan Shearer ch\u1eedi b\u1edbi VAR trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u00f2 h\u1ec1 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1, ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a. Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00f3 15 met v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. Ban \u0111\u1ea7u anh ta kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng VAR. Th\u1eadt l\u1ed1 b\u1ecbch, c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang b\u1ecb l\u1ea1m d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.&rdquo;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Didier Drogba chung quan \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Shearer, r\u1eb1ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o VAR. C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 m\u1edbi m\u1ebb n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u x\u1ea3y ra nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i kh\u00e1c, v\u00e0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm ra h\u01b0\u1edbng gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Alan Shearer ch\u1eedi b\u1edbi VAR kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 sai, n\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o k\u1ef3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/hong-pen-ronaldo-van-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-ky-luc-421-189564.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n</span> trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed (19 l\u1ea7n), d\u00f9 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111i h\u1ebft v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-santos-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-may-man-cua-bo-dao-nha-421-189570.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/hlv-santos-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-may-man-cua-bo-dao-nha.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-santos-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-may-man-cua-bo-dao-nha-421-189570.html\">HLV Santos n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a may m\u1eafn c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha?</span><br />\r\nV\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Fernando Santos chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Iran.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bat-luc-hlv-iran-len-tieng-doi-the-do-cho-ronaldo-421-189569.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/queiroz.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bat-luc-hlv-iran-len-tieng-doi-the-do-cho-ronaldo-421-189569.html\">B\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c, HLV Iran l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00f2i th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf cho Ronaldo</span><br />\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Iran m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 su\u00fdt n\u1eefa b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n. Sau tr\u1eadn, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Iran &ndash; HLV Carlos Queiroz \u0111\u00f2i ph\u1ea1t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf Ronaldo...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-461-189560.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/hong-pen-ronaldo-van-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-ky-luc.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-461-189560.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Iran 1-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)</span><br />\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Iran \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1 v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 25/6.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"588","checkdouble":"189575"},{"date":"07:02 26/06","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (26/6/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-2662018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Australia vs Peru trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Van Marwijk s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Australia v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nAustralia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018, song nh\u1eefng g\u00ec th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Van Marwijk th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai khi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Australia vs Peru (21h00 ng\u00e0y 2606) Hy v\u1ecdng mong manh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Australia vs Peru (21h00 ng\u00e0y 2606) Hy v\u1ecdng mong manh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Nhan-dinh-Australia-vs-Peru-(21h00-ngay-2606)-Hy-vong-mong-manh-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T Australia v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nMile Jedinak v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i khi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p r\u1eddi s\u00e2n sau 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-0, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 sau khi b\u1ecb thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, ph\u00fat 80 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba \u0111\u1eadp ch\u00e2n Aziz Behich bay v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi khi\u1ebfn Australia nh\u1eadn tr\u1eadn thua 1-2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p, Australia ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. Ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 7, Christian Eriksen \u0111\u00e3 tung c\u00fa volley ng\u1eabu h\u1ee9ng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Van Marwijk \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a Mile Jedinak \u1edf cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1. Trong hi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2, Australia t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn ngang ng\u1eeda v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng, Mile Jedinak v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7m nhi\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Kangaroo kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nAustralia vs Peru trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018. D\u00f9 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. T\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng C, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Australia vs Peru\" title=\"Preview Australia vs Peru\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Australia-vs-Peru.png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Australia vs Peru \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Australia s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Kangaroo \u0111ang k\u00e9m &ldquo;Nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa l\u00ednh ch\u00ec&rdquo; 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i Australia bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i Peru v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110an M\u1ea1ch m\u1edbi c\u00f3 hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nHi\u1ec7n Australia \u0111ang c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 (-1) trong khi \u0111\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch l\u00e0 (+1). N\u1ebfu \u0110an M\u1ea1ch thua Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 1 b\u00e0n, Australia th\u1eafng Peru v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 1 b\u00e0n. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec3m (4) v\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 (0).&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n h\u01a1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 2 tr\u1eadn. Mu\u1ed1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, Australia bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n h\u01a1n \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u1edf lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Australia th\u1eafng Peru, c\u00f2n \u0110an M\u1ea1ch thua Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb 2 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111i ti\u1ebfp nh\u1edd h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nWorld Cup 2006, Australia \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t \u0110\u1ee9c, NHM \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Kangaroo s\u1ebd t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 12 n\u0103m c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Zlatko Kranjcar.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Peru kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Australia vs Peru t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean Peru v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat, song th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Van Marwijk l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mot ngay that vong voi dai dien Nam My khi Phap loai Peru khoi World Cup 2018 bang chien thang toi thieu 1-0.\" title=\"M\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 khi Ph\u00e1p lo\u1ea1i Peru kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018 b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/thu-thanh-gallese-khang-dinh-dt-peru-chua-bo-cuoc.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Peru \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau 2 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Australia tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau 2 tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nPeru \u0111ang duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng World Cup, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 8 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 6 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, Peru c\u00f3 6/8 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n trong chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ricardo Gareca c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1edbi 27 l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng 11m nh\u01b0ng Christian Cueva l\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nD\u00f9 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m song Peru l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra non n\u1edbt v\u00e0 v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng, h\u1ecd thi\u1ebfu c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea1nh trong nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTr\u1eadn Australia vs Peru h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Peru s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec danh d\u1ef1. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i bi\u1ebft t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Australia vs Peru\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Australia vs Peru\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Australia-vs-Peru-(4-4-1-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Australia vs Peru</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: 2-1</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"587","checkdouble":"189576"},{"date":"07:12 26/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p (21h00 ng\u00e0y 26/6): C\u00e1i b\u1eaft tay c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00c2u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/Dan-Mach-vs-Phap.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018: M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 theo ch\u00e2n m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8. C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 ch\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ea7u h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean \u1edf Luzhniki.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Dan Mach vs Phap\" title=\"Preview \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Dan-Mach-vs-Phap.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Australia v\u00e0 Peru \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p s\u1edbm \u0111o\u1ea1t v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018, d\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec d\u00e0n sao \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Didier Deschamps \u0111ang ch\u1ecbu s\u1ee9c \u00e9p n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 v\u00ec nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thi\u1ebfu thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u \u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u00e2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p (21h00 ng\u00e0y 266) C\u00e1i b\u1eaft tay c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p (21h00 ng\u00e0y 266) C\u00e1i b\u1eaft tay c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Nhan-dinh-Dan-Mach-vs-Phap-(21h00-ngay-266)-Cai-bat-tay-cua-nguoi-Au-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng, c\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00e2ng cao c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 20 n\u0103m ch\u01b0a c\u1ea7n m\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u0129 di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u00e0 qu\u00ean \u0111i nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh to\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n knock-out h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n b\u1ea5t tr\u1eafc mu\u00f4n ph\u1ea7n. Nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 Griezmann, Mbappe, Pogba... c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb n\u00f3ng l\u00f2ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u00e2m l\u00fd hay l\u00e0n s\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1, Les Bleus c\u0169ng s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t lu\u00f4n c\u1ea3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0o tay \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea9y m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 trong v\u00f2ng 1/8, v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Croatia.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi 9 \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng g\u00ec cho Ph\u00e1p, khi h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7y r\u1eaby v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1i nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Christian Eriksen Dan Mach\" title=\"Christian Eriksen \u0110an M\u1ea1ch\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/christian-eriksen-dan-mach-co-the-dong-vai-phan-dien-khong-phai-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc \u00c2u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ef1c \u1ed5n khi tr\u1ea3i qua 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 v\u0169 b\u00e3o \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Peru trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n. Kasper Schmeichel ch\u1ec9 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty c\u1ee7a Australia m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00e1t huy s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p. C\u1ea7u h\u00f2a th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Ch\u1eb3ng may th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n cho h\u1ecd khi Australia kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u00e1nh th\u1eafng Australia nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Age Hareide kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ph\u00f3 m\u1eb7c v\u1eadn m\u1ec7nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o tay k\u1ebb kh\u00e1c khi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n h\u1ecd v\u1ed1n to\u00e0n quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110an M\u1ea1ch thu\u1ed9c d\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f4ng c\u00f9n th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Tr\u00ean h\u1ebft v\u1edbi t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ea7u h\u00f2a l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 cho \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 n\u00ean ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i b\u1eaft tay h\u00f2a nh\u00e3 gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng s\u00e1nh b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">World Cup 2018 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xep hang hien tai cua bang C World Cup 2018\" title=\"X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/C.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110an M\u1ea1ch (4-2-3-1): 1. Schmeichel; 14. Dalsgaard &ndash; 4. Kjaer &ndash; 6. Christensen &ndash; 17. Larsen; 8. Delaney &ndash; 19. Schone; 11. Braithwaite &ndash; 10. Eriksen &ndash; 23. Sisto; 9. Jorgensen<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1p (4-4-2): 16. Mandanda; 19. Sidibe &ndash; 4. Varane &ndash; 3. Kimpembe &ndash; 21. Hernandez; 11. Dembele &ndash; 15. N&rsquo;Zonzi &ndash; 13. Kante &ndash; 8. Lemar; 7. Griezmann &ndash; 9. Giroud<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p: 0-0\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Dan Mach vs Phap\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Dan-Mach-vs-Phap-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-4-2).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"586","checkdouble":"189577"},{"date":"07:12 26/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Argentina (1h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6): V\u1eeba \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3ng, v\u1eeba c\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/Nigeria-vs-Argentina.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Argentina b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018: Th\u1eafng c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7, Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i qu\u00e1 hi\u1ec3u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea5y, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n cho s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac c\u1ee7a Croatia trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng gi\u1edd.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Nigeria vs Argentina\" title=\"Preview Nigeria vs Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Nigeria-vs-Argentina.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Argentina b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 s\u1edf h\u1eefu trong tay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Argentina \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n qua hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf World Cup 2018 ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9o ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u00f9ng c\u1ef1c.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty h\u1ecfng \u0103n c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i kinh ho\u00e0ng ba b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia, m\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n m\u00e0 n\u00f3i Argentina kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. \u1ea4y v\u1eady m\u00e0 tr\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea5t v\u1eabn th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1ea1i cho h\u1ecd m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i sau cu\u1ed1i, khi Nigeria b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e1nh g\u1ee5c Iceland \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng D tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gi\u1edd th\u00ec ngo\u00e0i Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u, t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chia kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u l\u1eafm cho c\u1ea3 ba c\u00e1i t\u00ean kia, v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh m\u1ed9t Argentina \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ed5 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u. H\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng Nigeria \u0111\u00eam nay, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1edbn, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi hy v\u1ecdng Iceland kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Croatia s\u1ebd tung ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi xoay quanh th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nghi\u00eam t\u00fac.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi cung DT Argentina\" title=\"Messi cung DT Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/ngay-hom-nay-246.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Argentina b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u01a1 m\u00e0 h\u00e3y khoan b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng gi\u1edd gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Argentina v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e3 khi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nigeria c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i d\u1ec5 nh\u01b0 \u0103n s\u1eb5n cho h\u1ecd. Ch\u00ednh ra m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ee9c \u00e9p, \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u00e2m l\u00fd ng\u00fat ng\u00e0n v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 n\u1ea3y sinh trong c\u01a1n bi\u1ebfn lo\u1ea1n n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n cho hay, HLV Jorge Sampaoli \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 c\u00f2n Sergio Aguero, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb x\u1eed tr\u1ea3m. \u0110o\u00e0n k\u1ebft b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0103n ai, gi\u1edd Argentina s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ra sao v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng r\u1ed1i ren \u0111i\u00ean \u0111\u1ea3o nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2y? Li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua ngh\u1ecbch c\u1ea3nh v\u00e0 l\u00e1ch qua khe c\u1eeda si\u00eau h\u1eb9p tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft m\u00ecnh l\u00fac n\u00e0y?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Nigeria kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c m\u00e0 tr\u00e1i l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda v\u00f2ng 1/8 h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 Argentina khi ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a l\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland c\u00e0ng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Ch\u00e2u Phi t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 h\u1eebng h\u1ef1c kh\u00ed th\u1ebf b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u sinh t\u1eed.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nigeria thap sang co hoi di tiep\" title=\"Nigeria th\u1eafp s\u00e1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Gernot-Rohr-noi-ve-tran-Nigeria-vs-Iceland-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Argentina b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Argentina bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn, bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi c\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eabn v\u00f4 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng khi Croatia kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh nh\u1eb1m tr\u00e1nh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n gi\u00e0nh ba \u0111i\u1ec3m cho Iceland. L\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd n\u00f4n n\u00f3ng d\u00e2ng cao, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 s\u1ebd r\u01a1i v\u00e0o c\u00e1i b\u1eaby ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Nigeria gi\u0103ng ra ch\u1edd s\u1eb5n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh&rdquo; n\u00f3i g\u00ec th\u00ec n\u00f3i v\u1eabn thua k\u00e9m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1a nh\u01b0 con th\u00fa b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y v\u00e0o th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f9ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t. Nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ra Nigeria kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u1ecfi ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecbu s\u1ee9c \u00e9p kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 m\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb Argentina.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ed1t l\u00f5i v\u1eabn n\u1eb1m c\u1ea3 \u1edf Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u00e0 th\u00f4i, m\u1ed9t khi h\u1ecd g\u1ee1 r\u1ed1i trong c\u1ea3 kh\u00e2u t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng l\u1eabn ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 hay gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u0169ng quan tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m. H\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft, Argentina c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1edbi v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p, s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng ch\u1eb3ng l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 khi c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i s\u1edbm r\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i trong s\u1ef1 t\u1ee7i nh\u1ee5c b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m tr\u1eadn Croatia.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Argentina 1h00 ng\u00e0y 276 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Argentina 1h00 ng\u00e0y 276 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Nhan-dinh-Nigeria-vs-Argentina-1h00-ngay-276-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Argentina:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nigeria (3-5-2): 23. Uzoho; 6. Balogun &ndash; 5. Troost-Ekong &ndash; 22. Omeruo; 11. Moses &ndash; 4. Ndidi &ndash; 10. Mikel &ndash; 8. Etebo &ndash; 21. Ebuehi; 14. Iheanacho &ndash; 7. Musa<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Argentina (4-3-3): 12. Armani; 18. Salvio &ndash; 2. Mercado &ndash; 17. Otamendi &ndash; 3. Tagliafico; 7. Banega &ndash; 14. Mascherano &ndash; 15. Perez; 10. Messi &ndash; 9. Higuain &ndash; 11. Di Maria<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nigeria vs Argentina: 2-3\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Nigeria vs Argentina\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Nigeria vs Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Nigeria-vs-Argentina-(3-5-2-vs-4-3-3).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Nigeria vs Argentina</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"585","checkdouble":"189578"},{"date":"07:52 26/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Australia vs Peru (21h00 ng\u00e0y 26/06): C\u00f2n s\u1ed1ng l\u00e0 c\u00f2n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/nhan-dinh-australia-vs-peru-21h00-ngay-2606-con-song-la-con-chien-dau.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Australia vs Peru trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Van Marwijk s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Australia v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nAustralia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018, song nh\u1eefng g\u00ec th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Van Marwijk th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai khi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Australia vs Peru (21h00 ng\u00e0y 2606) Hy v\u1ecdng mong manh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Australia vs Peru (21h00 ng\u00e0y 2606) Hy v\u1ecdng mong manh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Nhan-dinh-Australia-vs-Peru-(21h00-ngay-2606)-Hy-vong-mong-manh-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T Australia v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nMile Jedinak v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i khi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p r\u1eddi s\u00e2n sau 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-0, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 sau khi b\u1ecb thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, ph\u00fat 80 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba \u0111\u1eadp ch\u00e2n Aziz Behich bay v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi khi\u1ebfn Australia nh\u1eadn tr\u1eadn thua 1-2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p, Australia ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. Ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 7, Christian Eriksen \u0111\u00e3 tung c\u00fa volley ng\u1eabu h\u1ee9ng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Van Marwijk \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a Mile Jedinak \u1edf cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1. Trong hi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2, Australia t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn ngang ng\u1eeda v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng, Mile Jedinak v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7m nhi\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Kangaroo kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nAustralia vs Peru trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018. D\u00f9 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. T\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng C, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Australia vs Peru\" title=\"Preview Australia vs Peru\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Australia-vs-Peru.png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Australia vs Peru \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Australia s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Kangaroo \u0111ang k\u00e9m &ldquo;Nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa l\u00ednh ch\u00ec&rdquo; 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i Australia bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i Peru v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110an M\u1ea1ch m\u1edbi c\u00f3 hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nHi\u1ec7n Australia \u0111ang c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 (-1) trong khi \u0111\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch l\u00e0 (+1). N\u1ebfu \u0110an M\u1ea1ch thua Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 1 b\u00e0n, Australia th\u1eafng Peru v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 1 b\u00e0n. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec3m (4) v\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 (0).&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n h\u01a1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 2 tr\u1eadn. Mu\u1ed1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, Australia bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n h\u01a1n \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u1edf lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Australia th\u1eafng Peru, c\u00f2n \u0110an M\u1ea1ch thua Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb 2 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111i ti\u1ebfp nh\u1edd h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nWorld Cup 2006, Australia \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t \u0110\u1ee9c, NHM \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Kangaroo s\u1ebd t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 12 n\u0103m c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Zlatko Kranjcar.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Peru kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Australia vs Peru t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean Peru v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat, song th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Van Marwijk l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mot ngay that vong voi dai dien Nam My khi Phap loai Peru khoi World Cup 2018 bang chien thang toi thieu 1-0.\" title=\"M\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 khi Ph\u00e1p lo\u1ea1i Peru kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018 b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/thu-thanh-gallese-khang-dinh-dt-peru-chua-bo-cuoc.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Peru \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau 2 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Australia tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau 2 tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nPeru \u0111ang duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng World Cup, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 8 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 6 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, Peru c\u00f3 6/8 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n trong chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ricardo Gareca c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1edbi 27 l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng 11m nh\u01b0ng Christian Cueva l\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nD\u00f9 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m song Peru l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra non n\u1edbt v\u00e0 v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng, h\u1ecd thi\u1ebfu c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea1nh trong nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTr\u1eadn Australia vs Peru h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Peru s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec danh d\u1ef1. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i bi\u1ebft t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Australia vs Peru\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Australia vs Peru\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Australia-vs-Peru-(4-4-1-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Australia vs Peru</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: 2-1</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"584","checkdouble":"189579"},{"date":"08:22 26/06","title":"Isco c\u00f3 v\u00e0i l\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/isco-co-vai-loi-muon-gui-den-dt-tay-ban-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Isco ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Ma R\u1ed1c, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a La Roja \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Isco kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi TBN b\u1ecb Ma R\u1ed1c c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 2-2</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p Ma R\u1ed1c, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i. Gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n tin r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Fernando Hierro s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, La Roja \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Isco ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Ma R\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Isco ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Ma R\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/isco-co-vai-loi-muon-gui-den-dt-tay-ban-nha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Isco ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Ma R\u1ed1c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 14, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 5 ph\u00fat sau Isco c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1. Kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian sau \u0111\u00f3 La Roja t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i song \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc, t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00fat 81, Youssef En-Nesyri b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-1 cho Ma R\u1ed1c, ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng b\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Iago Aspas m\u1edbi ghi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2 cho TBN. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-tay-ban-nha-vs-ma-roc-421-189558.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Ma R\u1ed1c</span> gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Fernando Hierro \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng B.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nIsco ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Ma R\u1ed1c, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a La Roja \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng mang v\u1ec1 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u1ea7n xem l\u1ea1i c\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 TBN \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Isco mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng B, T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. Isco kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh La Roja c\u1ea7n ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp trung \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Iniesta va Isco ghi ban cho TBN\" title=\"Iniesta va Isco ghi ban cho TBN\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-tbn-22-ma-roc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Isco mu\u1ed1n TBN ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nga s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ma R\u1ed1c, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 lu\u00f4n r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ch\u01a1i 100% phong \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Ma R\u1ed1c, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2 c\u1ee7a Iago Aspas \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn sau khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 video VAR. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, Isco chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00e0y mang l\u1ea1i l\u1ee3i \u00edch cho m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 T\u00e2y Ban Nha, t\u00f4i \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0a VAR v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"583","checkdouble":"189580"},{"date":"08:38 26/06","title":"\"V\u00ec danh d\u1ef1, Peru s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Australia\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/vi-danh-du-peru-se-lam-moi-cach-de-danh-bai-australia.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Paolo Guerrero ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Australia vs Peru, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 34 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec danh d\u1ef1.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Australia vs Peru \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng C</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nT\u1ed1i nay, Australia vs Peru trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cho ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paolo Guerrero ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Australia vs Peru h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Paolo Guerrero ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Australia vs Peru h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Paolo-Guerrero-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Australia-vs-Peru-hinh-anh.png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Australia vs Peru \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nAustralia m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai \u0111ang k\u00e9m \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Peru v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng \u0110an M\u1ea1ch thua Ph\u00e1p m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nC\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Australia l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 h\u1eb9p, nh\u01b0ng khi c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u00ec h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Bert van Marwijk \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Peru.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nC\u00f2n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau 2 tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p, song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec danh d\u1ef1, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Nga v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 trong tay.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Paolo Guerrero quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Australia</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Paolo Guerrero ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-australia-vs-peru-21h00-ngay-2606-con-song-la-con-chien-dau-421-189579.html\" target=\"_blank\">Australia vs Peru</span>, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 34 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec danh d\u1ef1.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Guerrero phat bieu ve tran Australia vs Peru\" title=\"Guerrero ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Australia vs Peru\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/vi-danh-du-peru-se-lam-moi-cach-de-danh-bai-australia.PNG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Guerrero ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Australia vs Peru</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, nh\u01b0ng Peru v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec danh d\u1ef1. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi\u1ebfn NHM th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n&ldquo;Peru mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi r\u1eddi Nga, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Australia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. V\u1edbi th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nPaolo Guerrero \u0111\u00e3 ghi 34 b\u00e0n sau 88 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Peru, anh \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T Australia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng cao th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG ngay \u1edf World Cup 2018, t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Australia&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"582","checkdouble":"189581"},{"date":"08:27 26/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iceland vs Croatia, (01h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6): Kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/nhan-dinh-iceland-vs-croatia-01h00-ngay-276-kho-co-bat-ngo.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y sau hai th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria v\u00e0 Argentina. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Iceland \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u1ea9n s\u1ed1 sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria, li\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam \u00c2u c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m?</h2><h1 style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; line-height: 21pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h1>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Croatia \u2013 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u00e1p l\u1ef1c<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u, thi \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u t\u00ednh th\u1ef1c chi\u1ebfn, \u0110T Croatia \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria v\u00e0 Argentina. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o c\u1edd Ca-r\u00f4 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u0111\u1eadm n\u00e9t v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u1edbi 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o. Trong \u0111\u00f3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u00e0n h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ebfc tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Argentina v\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu Croatia s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi cho d\u00f9 HLV Zlatko Dalic c\u00f3 tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb nh\u1eb1m gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iceland vs Croatia (01h00 ng\u00e0y 276) Kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iceland vs Croatia (01h00 ng\u00e0y 276) Kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Iceland-vs-Croatia.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0o s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra cho tr\u1eadn Iceland vs Croatia v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Iceland vs Croatia t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 nhau khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i n\u1eb1m c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Iceland th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng chung cu\u1ed9c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean trong l\u1ea7n t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c. Croatia \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u00f2n Iceland l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng D v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8. Khi m\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 Croatia gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi, \u0110T Croatia ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1eafc ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ngay c\u1ea3 khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, \u0110T Croatia v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D nh\u1edd hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Croatia s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u m\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u00e1p l\u1ef1c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng nh\u1eb1m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng s\u1ee9c cho v\u00f2ng 1/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Iceland \u2013 li\u1ec7u c\u00f2n k\u1ef3 t\u00edch?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai v\u1eeba qua, \u0110T Iceland \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Nigeria thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, ph\u00f3ng kho\u00e1ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ea3o b\u0103ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 h\u1ee5t h\u01a1i v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c song c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 B\u0103ng \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9m may. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Iceland \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 10 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 qu\u1ea3 11m h\u1ecfng \u0103n c\u1ee7a Sigurdsson ph\u00fat 83. Do \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Aron Gunnarsson r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Croatia l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cau chuyen ve nhung chien binh Iceland qua cam\" title=\"C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh Iceland qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Nhan-dinh-Iceland-vs-Nigeria-Chien-binh-hay-Dai-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh Iceland qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, Iceland bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ee7 l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina ph\u1ea3i mang t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Heimir Hallgrimsson. N\u1ebfu Argentina kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng, Iceland s\u1ebd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i. N\u1ebfu Lionel Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1edfi ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Iceland \u1edf th\u1ebf ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh n\u00e0y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ea3o ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 khi ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, c\u00f2n n\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng th\u00ec h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt s\u01a1 h\u1edf. Tuy nhi\u00ean trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 t\u00edch v\u1eabn th\u01b0\u1eddng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Iceland t\u1eebng vi\u1ebft n\u00ean c\u00e2u truy\u1ec7n c\u1ed5 t\u00edch t\u1ea1i EURO 2016. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i t\u1eadp 2 c\u1ee7a c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ed5 t\u00edch \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ebfu Iceland \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia c\u00f2n Argentina ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00eam nay<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>L\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai \u0111\u1ed9i:</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Ragnar Sigurdsson ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ra s\u00e2n cho Iceland sau khi g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nigeria. Johann Berg Gudmunsson c\u0169ng \u0111ang g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Croatia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0 Ivan Rakitic, Mario Mandzukic\u2026 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn 1 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng \u1edf 2 tr\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Luka Modric c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Iceland vs Croatia\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Iceland vs Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Iceland-vs-Croatia-(4-4-1-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Iceland vs Croatia</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n:\u00a01-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#111111;mso-fareast-language:ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"581","checkdouble":"189583"},{"date":"08:32 26/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh (18h00 ng\u00e0y 26/6): \u0110\u00f2i n\u1ee3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/8/nhan-dinh-hagl-vs-than-quang-ninh-18h00-ngay-266-doi-no-duoc-khong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CLB HAGL v\u1eeba t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1ch c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u1edf v\u00f2ng 15 v\u1eeba qua.Tuy nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u1edf tr\u1eadn HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh?</h2><h2>HAGL \u2013 ch\u1ee7 kh\u00e1t 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-2 \u0111\u1ea7y v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 ghi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai c\u1eaft \u0111\u1ee9t chu\u1ed7i 3 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap HAGL c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean BXH m\u00e0 n\u00f3 c\u00f2n ti\u1ebfp th\u00eam s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin, t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu l\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i 26/6.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh (18h00 ng\u00e0y 266) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh (18h00 ng\u00e0y 266) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Nhan-dinh-HAGL-vs-Than-Quang-Ninh-(18h00-ngay-266)-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HAGL \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i C\u1ea9m Ph\u1ea3 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u2018G\u1ed7\u2019 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f2n h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 chung cu\u1ed9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea7n t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nguy c\u01a1 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf h\u1eefu d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kinh nghi\u1ec7m, Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 t\u1ecf ra m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n HAGL m\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Do \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng G\u1ed7 ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 ch\u1eaft chiu c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u00ec may ra h\u1ecd m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i\u00a0 b\u00f3ng x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean BXH V-League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng b\u1ecf xa tr\u00ean BXH. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 15, Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1ecf xa v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch\u2026 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1-4 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i h\u00f4m 13/6 v\u1eeba qua, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng t\u1ecf ra h\u1ee5t h\u01a1i trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch l\u00e0 v\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1eafng 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2/6 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. C\u00f2n l\u1ea1i h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 thua 2 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ho\u00e0 2 tr\u1eadn. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch Sanna Kh\u00e1nh Ho\u00e0 trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1ea1t nho\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1eadp ph\u00f9 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh c\u00f2n \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n \u1edf m\u1ed7i chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch. Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch trong 6 tr\u1eadn thi \u0111\u1ea5u xa qu\u00ea, ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i Pleiku l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 n\u01a1i m\u00e0 HAGL \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y khi h\u1ecd m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u00fang 1 tr\u1eadn duy nh\u1ea5t trong 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HAGL vs Than Quang Ninh\" title=\"HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/8/truc-tiep-quang-ninh-vs-hagl-18h00-ngay-96-vleague-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Tr\u1eadn HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-2 t\u1ea1i Pleiku. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 5-0 \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh kh\u00f4ng tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u1edf c\u00fap QG. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c hi v\u1ecdng th\u00eam v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean BXH.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a HAGL, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh v\u1eeba m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 th\u00eam h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 Osmar. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng SLNA, nh\u01b0ng HLV Minh Ninh v\u1eabn tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho s\u00e2n Pleiku hi v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o m\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean G\u1ed7 s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t 3 n\u1ed9i binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eadp trung \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00ec th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t l\u00e0 V\u0103n Thanh, T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0 V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh. N\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i V-League 2018, HAGL \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 26 l\u1ea7n. \u0110\u00f3 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn v\u1edbi G\u1ed7 trong m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 5 khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng s\u1edbm c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n nh\u01b0ng so s\u00e1nh gi\u1eefa t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00ec hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 ch\u1eaft chiu c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, HAGL may ra m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 18h00 t\u1ed1i nay 26/6 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. M\u1eddi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd theo d\u00f5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u:</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 11 tr\u1eadn, HAGL th\u1eafng 4, h\u00f2a 2, thua 5.<br>\r\n- Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HAGL, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 th\u1eafng 3, h\u00f2a 1, thua 1.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL:\u00a0V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn; \u0110\u00f4ng Tri\u1ec1u, Anh T\u00e0i, H\u1ed3ng Duy, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0110\u1ee9c L\u01b0\u01a1ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, V\u0103n Thanh, Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng, Osmar, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\nQu\u1ea3ng Ninh:\u00a0Tu\u1ea5n Linh; Thanh H\u00e0o, Thanh Hi\u1ec1n, Xu\u00e2n H\u00f9ng, Vi\u1ebft Tri\u1ec1u, Nguy\u00ean Sa, Xu\u00e2n T\u00fa, H\u1ea3i Huy, Nh\u1eadt Minh, Eydison, H\u1ed3ng Qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Roboto-Regular, serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"580","checkdouble":"189584"},{"date":"03:21 26/06","title":"HLV Nga: \u201c\u0110\u00e3 bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/hlv-nga-da-biet-truoc-chung-toi-van-bat-luc-truoc-uruguay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Cherchesov ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Uruguay 3-0 Nga. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, Nga v\u1eabn b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n 3 b\u00e0n thua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Nga th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNga \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng A c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi Uruguay. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Saudi Arabia 5-1 v\u00e0 Ai C\u1eadp 3-1 \u0111\u1ea7y thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng A.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng Saudi Arabia v\u00e0 Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec1u x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean Nga tr\u00ean BXH FIFA song h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Uruguay x\u1ebfp 14 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 x\u1ee9 b\u1ea1ch d\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng mong ch\u1edd \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. Ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 m\u01a1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Nga \u0110\u00e3 bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Nga \u0110\u00e3 bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/HLV-Nga-Da-biet-truoc,-chung-toi-van-bat-luc-truoc-Uruguay-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nga th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 3 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay, Nga \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf. H\u1ecd thua chung cu\u1ed9c 3 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 b\u1edfi c\u00e1c pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Luis Suarez, Edinson Cavani b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh 1 pha ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Denis Cheryshev. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf m\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Igor Smolnikov c\u1ee7a Nga nh\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn cho th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd th\u00eam \u00ea ch\u1ec1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Cherchesov ch\u1ec9 ra nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Cherchesov ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Uruguay 3-0 Nga. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 54 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh, Nga v\u1eabn b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Cherchesov\" title=\"HLV Cherchesov\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/hlv-nga-da-biet-truoc-chung-toi-van-bat-luc-truoc-uruguay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Cherchesov ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Uruguay 3-0 Nga \u0111\u1ea7y cay \u0111\u1eafng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;<em>Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp h\u00f4m qua, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh 20 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp c\u00e1c b\u00e0i \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t. V\u00e0 h\u00f4m nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. M\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf m\u1ea1nh ri\u00eang. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o n\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n</em>&rdquo;, Cherchesov n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;<em>Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i kh\u00e1ch quan. \u00c1p l\u1ef1c m\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1edbn</em>.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Nga tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng th\u1ee9 2 t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng A v\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. HLV Cherchesov n\u00f3i th\u00eam: &ldquo;<em>Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n cho c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chu \u0111\u00e1o nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3</em>.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Uruguay 3-0 Nga tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-tabarez-phat-bieu-sau-tran-uruguay-30-nga-421-189561.html\">HLV Uruguay n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n v\u00f9i d\u1eadp ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-uruguay-30-nga-421-189559.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay 3-0 Nga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-uruguay-vs-nga-461-189550.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Uruguay 3-0 Nga (B\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-uruguay-vs-nga-463-189532.html\">Uruguay 3-0 Nga (KT): H\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t g\u1ea5u Nga, La Celeste to\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"579","checkdouble":"189563"},{"date":"05:25 26/06","title":"H\u1ecfng pen, Ronaldo v\u1eabn gi\u00fap World Cup 2018 l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/diem-nhan-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-noi-that-vong-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong hi\u1ec7p 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea3o Iberia h\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, qua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn World Cup 2018 l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 pen trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nN\u01b0\u1edbc Nga &ldquo;ph\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea3o&rdquo; v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, v\u1edbi qu\u1ea3 11m c\u1ee7a Ronaldo trong <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-463-189553.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 gi\u1eefa Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span>, k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 ghi nh\u1eadn s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng penalty k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c &ndash; 19 l\u1ea7n t\u00ednh t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i. Con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh, k\u1ef3 World Cup 2014 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Brazil ch\u1ec9 ghi nh\u1eadn 13 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n to\u00e0n gi\u1ea3i. Trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u qu\u1ea3 11m nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn nay (18 l\u1ea7n) v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1990, sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c san b\u1eb1ng \u1edf c\u00e1c n\u0103m 1998 v\u00e0 2002.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, x\u1ee9 s\u1edf b\u1ea1ch d\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1ecdi k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, d\u00f9 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u01b0a \u0111i qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i \u0111\u00e3 ra t\u0103ng, m\u00e0 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a VAR. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 video g\u1ed3m t\u1ed5 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng ekip b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh), kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ecf qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"World Cup 2018 l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 pen \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ed5i\" title=\"Ronaldo h\u1ecfng pen\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/diem-nhan-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-noi-that-vong-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>World Cup 2018&nbsp;l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 pen \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ed5i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVAR v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 sau. To\u00e0n b\u1ed9 clip \u1edf m\u1ecdi g\u00f3c quay s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem x\u00e9t k\u1ef9 trong ph\u00f2ng video b\u1edfi 4 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i chu\u1ea9n FIFA, trong m\u1ecdi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng. V\u00e0 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 khi n\u00e0o tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng tr\u00f9ng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 VAR, \u00f4ng s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o, sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f9y t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1y ra ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i qua b\u0103ng h\u00ecnh. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean trong m\u1ecdi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7 CR7 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u00fat h\u1ecfng. D\u00f9 sao, \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 pen \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ed5i, v\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat nh\u01b0 Ronaldo v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, n\u1ebfu c\u0103n c\u1ee9 theo nh\u1eefng g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i, s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng penalty cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga s\u1ebd c\u00f2n g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i, g\u1ea5p ba con s\u1ed1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/hazard-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-sieu-ky-luc-sau-64-nam-421-189367.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018 c\u0169ng ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u00ec ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</span>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-421-189557.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/clip-ban-thang-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-421-189557.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nChuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-461-189560.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/hong-pen-ronaldo-van-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-ky-luc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-461-189560.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Iran 1-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)<br>\r\n</span>\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Iran \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1 v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 25/6.<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"578","checkdouble":"189564"},{"date":"06:51 26/06","title":"4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau m\u00e0n \u201ch\u00fat ch\u1ebft\u201d c\u1ee7a TBN tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ma R\u1ed1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/diem-nhan-tay-ban-nha-vs-ma-roc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Iran m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 su\u00fdt n\u1eefa b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n. Sau tr\u1eadn, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Iran \u2013 HLV Carlos Queiroz \u0111\u00f2i ph\u1ea1t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf Ronaldo v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nRonaldo \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i vung tay v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t Morteza Pouraliganji c\u1ee7a Iran. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nghi ng\u1edd g\u00ec v\u1ec1 pha \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng n\u00e0y, khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng VAR \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean sau kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00ec theo d\u00f5i b\u0103ng h\u00ecnh, v\u1ecb vua \u00e1o \u0111en quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 trao cho Ronaldo m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng. Trong t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 1-0, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Iran \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ed3n l\u00ean v\u00e0 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i. B\u1edfi v\u1eady n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf, ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra khi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 10 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, HLV Carlos Queiroz c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng: &ldquo;Theo lu\u1eadt, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n gi\u1eadt ch\u1ecf v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0103n th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf, kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 Messi hay Ronaldo. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra khi \u0111\u00f3. C\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ai ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m. Khi c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0o s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ebfn VAR, ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft ai l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Carlos Queiroz doi phat the do Ronaldo\" title=\"HLV Carlos Queiroz \u0111\u00f2i ph\u1ea1t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/red.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Carlos Queiroz \u0111\u00f2i ph\u1ea1t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf Ronaldo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;VAR l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng kh\u00e1 m\u01a1 h\u1ed3, v\u00e0 th\u00fa th\u1ef1c t\u00f4i v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng t\u00e0i n\u00e0o hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, b\u0103ng ghi h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u l\u00fd do g\u00ec tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1edbt l\u1edd. Khi b\u1ea1n l\u00e0m gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec m\u1ed9t pha th\u00fac c\u00f9i ch\u1ecf, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra hay kh\u00f4ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu n\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf - nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n ra trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Carlos Queiroz \u0111\u00f2i ph\u1ea1t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf cho Ronaldo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha s\u1ebd th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Uruguay, trong khi Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1eabn b\u00ecnh y\u00ean v\u00f4 s\u1ef1 khi ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-461-189560.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/hong-pen-ronaldo-van-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-ky-luc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-461-189560.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Iran 1-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Iran \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1 v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 25/6.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hong-pen-ronaldo-van-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-ky-luc-421-189564.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/diem-nhan-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-noi-that-vong-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hong-pen-ronaldo-van-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-ky-luc-421-189564.html\">H\u1ecfng pen, Ronaldo v\u1eabn gi\u00fap World Cup 2018 l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c</span><br>\r\nTrong hi\u1ec7p 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea3o Iberia h\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, qua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn World Cup 2018 l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 pen trong...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"577","checkdouble":"189565"},{"date":"04:06 26/06","title":"Suarez \"n\u1ed5\" t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng sau khi \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i Nga","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/suarez-no-tung-bung-sau-khi-da-bai-nga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Luis Suarez mong mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u00f9ng Uruguay sau khi l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf World Cup n\u0103m nay.</h2><h2>Suarez l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Suarez \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n gi\u00fap Uruguay gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Uruguay \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n trong 3 k\u1ef3 World Cup li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Suarez ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga h\u00f4m qua. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u cho <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-uruguay-vs-nga-463-189532.htmlabc\" target=\"_blank\">m\u00e0n v\u00f9i d\u1eadp ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Uruguay.</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Suarez n\u1ed5 t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng sau khi Uruguay \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Suarez n\u1ed5 t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng sau khi Uruguay \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/suarez-no-tung-bung-sau-khi-da-bai-nga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Suarez n\u1ed5 to sau khi gi\u00fap Uruguay \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nga</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Suarez t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Nh\u01b0ng anh c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o Uruguay l\u1eadp th\u00eam nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cM\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u0111i t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a World Cup. Nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c sinh ra l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1. \u1ede c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi \u0111ang \u0111i \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u1edbi v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cSau khi th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-0, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00f4m nay. T\u00f4i m\u1eebng v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. B\u1edfi v\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Uruguay th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf World Cup v\u00e0 n\u1eafm gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n, ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>L\u00fd do Uruguay ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Uruguay b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nga v\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i sau khi \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm ch\u1eafc t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Oscar Tabarez \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ef1 do h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 Suarez cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cNh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng h\u00f4m nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn kh\u00e1c h\u1eb3n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u00edt b\u1ecb \u00e1p l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n v\u00e0 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u1edf tr\u00ean s\u00e2n\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</em><strong><em>Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay vs Nga:</em></strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-uruguay-vs-nga-461-189550.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Uruguay 3-0 Nga (B\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs Nga:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-tabarez-phat-bieu-sau-tran-uruguay-30-nga-421-189561.html\">HLV Uruguay n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n v\u00f9i d\u1eadp ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bang-xep-hang-bxh-bang-a-world-cup-2018-421-189547.html\">B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng chung cu\u1ed9c b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"576","checkdouble":"189566"},{"date":"04:42 26/06","title":"Salah nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i sau chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/salah-nhan-loi-sau-chien-dich-world-cup-tham-hoa-cua-ai-cap.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mohamed Salah \u0111\u00e3 xin l\u1ed7i c\u00e1c C\u0110V sau khi Ai C\u1eadp b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018 ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 n\u00e0o.</h2><h2>Ai C\u1eadp b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Salah b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</span> khi m\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ecbp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1edbi Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp g\u1eb7p Uruguay. Anh ghi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u1edbt ch\u00fat \u00edt danh d\u1ef1 cho Ai C\u1eadp \u1edf tr\u1eadn thua ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah xin l\u1ed7i C\u0110V Ai C\u1eadp sau chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Salah xin l\u1ed7i C\u0110V Ai C\u1eadp sau chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/salah-nhan-loi-sau-chien-dich-world-cup-tham-hoa-cua-ai-cap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Salah xin l\u1ed7i C\u0110V\u00a0Ai C\u1eadp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Salah \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. Ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng m\u1edf \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1edbm cho Ai C\u1eadp v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tinh t\u1ebf v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Saudi Arabia. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng v\u00e0 r\u1eddi cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTruy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nga \u0111\u01b0a tin r\u1eb1ng ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra c\u00e3i c\u1ecd sau khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac. V\u00e0 Salah l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n l\u00ean xe bus c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng sau \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y c\u0169ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c C\u0110V Ai C\u1eadp s\u1ebd tha th\u1ee9 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n xin l\u1ed7i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c C\u0110V Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi t\u1eadn n\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft l\u00e0 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi h\u1ecd, c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u00e2y gi\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o World Cup sau 28 n\u0103m. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2022\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Salah kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0110TQG</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Hector Cuper \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n d\u1eadp tan tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng Salah s\u1ebd t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ai C\u1eadp sau tr\u1eadn thua Saudi Arabia. Nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng c\u0169ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn t\u1ea1i sao c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ecbp bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft t\u1ea1i sao Salah kh\u00f4ng tham d\u1ef1 h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 b\u00e1c s\u0129 nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00fd do c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 \u01b0? T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft \u00fd c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 g\u00ec. Theo nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 Salah s\u1ebd t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 tin \u0111\u1ed3n hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt b\u1edfi v\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110TQG\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Saudi Arabia vs Ai C\u1eadp:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-saudi-arabia-vs-ai-cap-461-189549.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Saudi Arabia 2-1 Ai C\u1eadp (B\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Saudi Arabia vs Ai C\u1eadp:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bang-xep-hang-bxh-bang-a-world-cup-2018-421-189547.html\">B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng chung cu\u1ed9c b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-saudi-arabia-vs-ai-cap-421-189538.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Saudi Arabia vs Ai C\u1eadp tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"575","checkdouble":"189567"},{"date":"06:07 26/06","title":"B\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c, HLV Iran l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00f2i th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf cho Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/queiroz.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Iran m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 su\u00fdt n\u1eefa b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n. Sau tr\u1eadn, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Iran \u2013 HLV Carlos Queiroz \u0111\u00f2i ph\u1ea1t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf Ronaldo v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nRonaldo \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i vung tay v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t Morteza Pouraliganji c\u1ee7a Iran. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nghi ng\u1edd g\u00ec v\u1ec1 pha \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng n\u00e0y, khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng VAR \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean sau kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00ec theo d\u00f5i b\u0103ng h\u00ecnh, v\u1ecb vua \u00e1o \u0111en quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 trao cho Ronaldo m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng. Trong t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 1-0, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Iran \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ed3n l\u00ean v\u00e0 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i. B\u1edfi v\u1eady n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf, ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra khi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 10 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, HLV Carlos Queiroz c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng: &ldquo;Theo lu\u1eadt, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n gi\u1eadt ch\u1ecf v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0103n th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf, kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 Messi hay Ronaldo. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra khi \u0111\u00f3. C\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ai ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m. Khi c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0o s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ebfn VAR, ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft ai l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Carlos Queiroz doi phat the do Ronaldo\" title=\"HLV Carlos Queiroz \u0111\u00f2i ph\u1ea1t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/red.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Carlos Queiroz \u0111\u00f2i ph\u1ea1t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf Ronaldo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;VAR l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng kh\u00e1 m\u01a1 h\u1ed3, v\u00e0 th\u00fa th\u1ef1c t\u00f4i v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng t\u00e0i n\u00e0o hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, b\u0103ng ghi h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u l\u00fd do g\u00ec tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1edbt l\u1edd. Khi b\u1ea1n l\u00e0m gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec m\u1ed9t pha th\u00fac c\u00f9i ch\u1ecf, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra hay kh\u00f4ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu n\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf - nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n ra trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Carlos Queiroz \u0111\u00f2i ph\u1ea1t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf cho Ronaldo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha s\u1ebd th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Uruguay, trong khi Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1eabn b\u00ecnh y\u00ean v\u00f4 s\u1ef1 khi ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-461-189560.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/hong-pen-ronaldo-van-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-ky-luc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-461-189560.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Iran 1-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Iran \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1 v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 25/6.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hong-pen-ronaldo-van-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-ky-luc-421-189564.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/diem-nhan-iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-noi-that-vong-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hong-pen-ronaldo-van-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-ky-luc-421-189564.html\">H\u1ecfng pen, Ronaldo v\u1eabn gi\u00fap World Cup 2018 l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c</span><br>\r\nTrong hi\u1ec7p 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea3o Iberia h\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, qua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn World Cup 2018 l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 pen trong...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"574","checkdouble":"189569"}]}